snippet.title: Johnny Depp's Friends Reveal How Amber Heard Destroyed Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's Friends Reveal How Amber Heard Destroyed Johnny Depp 
Johnny Depp's friends have revealed exactly how Amber Heard has destroyed Johnny. We know that the libel case between Johnny and Amber may just be looking to shift to Johnny's favor, but we're still a long way from anything positive. At the end of the day, Amber Heard is prepping up for her new Aquaman movies while Johnny Depp was forcibly removed from the role that made him who he is today. And that is all despite the fact that most of Amber's claims have been debunked and, in fact, have even come back to herself.
